wing
information is included on the ETA Form 9142 - Application for Temporary
Employment Certification and must be accurately stated by the employer:</p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'text-indent:-.25in'><span>(1)<span
